</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-51_ pf-text-1"><strong>Disinfection</strong> - Apply a gentle antiseptic to reduce risk of infection.






</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-53_ pf-text-1"><strong>Dressing</strong> - Cover the wound with a sterile bandage.








</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-55_ pf-text-1"><strong>Medical assessment</strong> - Seek professional medical advice, especially if the skin is significantly broken.









